change plan.</Instruction>\n  </Step>\n  <Step number=\"5\" title=\"Execute Implementation\">\n    <Instruction>Apply planned changes using appropriate tools. Ensure all relevant files are in context before modifications.</Instruction>\n  </Step>\n  <Step number=\"6\" title=\"Verify Changes\">\n    <Instruction>Use available tools like linters or type checkers. Analyze outcomes and iterate to fix errors.</Instruction>\n  </Step>\n  <Step number=\"7\" title=\"Assess Task Completion\">\n    <Instruction>Evaluate whether completion conditions are met; loop back if not.</Instruction>\n  </Step>\n  <Step number=\"8\" title=\"Final Summary\">\n    <Instruction>Summarize actions and confirm the overarching goal is achieved. list next actions if any.</Instruction>\n  </Step>\n</Workflow>\n\n</AiderDeskSystemPrompt>\n"},{"role":"user","content":"Use the glob tool to find files matching '*.gemspec' in the project. Report what you find."},{"role":"assistant","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_5eedf4d930ff4d2f9d3d5895","type":"function","function":{"name":"power---glob","arguments":"{\"pattern\":\"*.gemspec\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/ericsmith66/development/legion\"}"}}],"content":"(Tool call requested: power---glob)"},{"role":"tool","tool_call_id":"call_5eedf4d930ff4d2f9d3d5895","content":""}],"tools":[{"type":"function","function":{"name":"power---file_read","description":"Reads and returns the content of a specified non-binary file. Useful for inspecting file contents when analyzing user's request or before modifying it. Can return content as raw text or with line numbers in format 'lineNumber|content'. Supports line offset and limit for reading specific portions of files.","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"file_path":{"type":"string"},"with_lines":{"type":"boolean","default":false},"line_offset":{"type":"integer","default":0,"minimum":0},"line_limit":{"type":"integer","default":1000,"minimum":1}},"required":["file_path"],"additionalProperties":false}}},{"type":"function","functio