dependencies_score\\\": 2,\\n    \\\"depends_on\\\": [1],\\n    \\\"notes\\\": \\\"Implementation — depends on test task 1. Wraps gem's CallbackBus, persists to WorkflowEvent\\\"\\n  },\\n  {\\n    \\\"position\\\": 3,\\n    \\\"type\\\": \\\"test\\\",\\n    \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"Write integration tests in test/integration/postgres_bus_integration_test.rb. Test full cycle: create WorkflowRun, create PostgresBus, publish multiple events, verify Workfl"}}}
