 \\\"concepts_score\\\": 4,\\n    \\\"dependencies_score\\\": 4,\\n    \\\"depends_on\\\": [],\\n    \\\"notes\\\": \\\"Test task — depends on existing models but not on AgentAssemblyService\\\"\\n  },\\n  {\\n    \\\"position\\\": 4,\\n    \\\"type\\\": \\\"code\\\",\\n    \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"Implement DispatchService in app/services/legion/dispatch_service.rb. The service must coordinate the full dispatch flow, including verbose event streaming, WorkflowRun creation/updating, and error han"}}}
