ion — depends on unit tests from task 1\\\"\\n  },\\n  {\\n    \\\"position\\\": 3,\\n    \\\"type\\\": \\\"test\\\",\\n    \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"Write integration tests for team import flow: import from fixture directory mirroring real .aider-desk structure, verify to_profile returns valid Profile objects, test re-import preserves membership IDs while updating configs, and verify transaction rollback on injected DB errors leaves no partial records.\\"}}}
