ite comprehensive unit tests for OrchestratorHooksService covering all 4 hooks: iteration budget (warn at threshold, block at 2x, model-specific thresholds), context pressure (60% at_risk, 80% decomposing+blocked), handoff capture (creates continuation WorkflowRun with metadata chain), cost enforcement (blocks with budget_exceeded status). Include error resilience tests and registration idempotency.\\\",\\n    \\\"agent\\\": \\\"rails-lead\\\",\\n    \\\"files_s"}}}
