"Implementation of config and service — depends on unit test task 1\\\"\\n  },\\n  {\\n    \\\"position\\\": 3,\\n    \\\"type\\\": \\\"test\\\",\\n    \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"Write integration tests in test/integration/orchestrator_hooks_integration_test.rb, covering full dispatch scenarios with low iteration limit leading to iteration_limit status, hook activity recorded in WorkflowRun metadata, and handoff triggering creation of continuation Workfl"}}}
