un updates, and error handling to make tests from Task 1 pass.\\\",\\n    \\\"agent\\\": \\\"rails-lead\\\",\\n    \\\"files_score\\\": 1,\\n    \\\"concepts_score\\\": 4,\\n    \\\"dependencies_score\\\": 3,\\n    \\\"depends_on\\\": [1, 2],\\n    \\\"notes\\\": \\\"Implementation — depends on configuration and tests\\\"\\n  },\\n  {\\n    \\\"position\\\": 4,\\n    \\\"type\\\": \\\"test\\\",\\n    \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"Write integration tests for OrchestratorHooks in full dispatch flow, ver"}}}
